text: Absolutely loved my experience at Meet Bar! The beautiful lady boss was incredibly warm and welcoming, which made the visit even more enjoyable. The prices are very reasonable, making it great value for money. The cozy and inviting environment is perfect for relaxing or catching up with friends. Highly recommend this gem to anyone looking for a great spot to unwind!
Cosy nice place for to meet and chill with great prices!
Nice & fun place to hang out. Have darts and ktv is very good. Drinks are cheap too! Had great fun! Staff very friendly, will definitely go back!
Nice and cosy pub. Friendly staff and good KTV system.
